    "input": {
      "body": "Final issue resolution:\n\nAfter documenting the attempted implementation in PR #28, we are **closing as not planned** because the ESM migration is blocked by **architectural constraints** in the current JavaScript demo and harmony core integration.\n\nThe **future implementation blocked** status is due to CommonJS-oriented module loading, tokenization initialization assumptions, and bundler compatibility issues that cannot be fixed safely at the demo layer alone. A successful ESM migration **requires core redesign** of the module boundary and explicit support for modern module exports before this enhancement can be revisited.",
      "issue_number": 27,
      "owner": "mangowhoiscloud",
      "repo": "harmony"
    },
